name: 'Seomra Codlata' 'The Bedroom' Irish language handpulled screenprint / Made in Ireland
description:
A beautiful Irish language handpulled screenprint for the bedroom.

This print says 'Seomra Codlata', which is Irish for 'The Bedroom'. It measures 420 x 297 mm	or 16.5 x 11.7 in and so fits perfectly inside an A3 frame. It is printed in weathered white ink on heavyweight & high quality 300gsm black paper card.

This print is one of only 10 produced so it is very exclusive. Only 10 of this design in these colours will ever be printed.

* All of our prints come unframed. They are posted in a sturdy postal tube to ensure they reach you in perfect condition. All prints are signed & numbered by the artist. Note: As these are handpulled screenprints, each one is slightly different. Because they are unique they may vary a little from the print pictured.
